Befriending Critters: Bird in the Hand
Radagast the Brown asks you help him rescue birds and bring them back to the safety of Rhosgobel.

'Ah, thank you! I see you were able to bring back a couple of birds with you. I am glad your travels were a success.\n\n'You have a good rapport with the animals. This skill will aid you on your journeys ahead.'
